        <h2>Poncho sends you notifications about weather nearby!</h2>

        <br />

        <h3>How does it work?</h3>
        <p>The Poncho iPhone app runs in the background 
        and uses the excellent <a href="https://developer.darkskyapp.com/docs">Dark Sky weather API</a> to give you micro-weather notifications based on your location.</p>

        <br />

        <h3>How was it built?</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Poncho uses the <a href="https://developers.geoloqi.com/titanium">Geoloqi SDK</a>.</li>
          <li>and was built using the <a href="http://appcelerator.com">Titanium</a> framework</li>
          <li>You can <a href="https://github.com/geoloqi/PonchoApp">download the source code</a> here to make your own weather application!</li>
        </ul>

        <br />

